comments.body: Google search results summarize as many parameters as they can, it can come from everyone's search history resulting in a trending keyword.I have never heard of any information about the BTC address above. It may have been suspected of being involved in fraudulent operations, hacking a platform, or something else in the past that attracted the attention of many people to search for it on the Google search engine even though it was actually just an empty address.
